The '''Green Line''' is a development corridor in [[Downtown Atlanta]] stretching from [[Georgia International Plaza]] in the west, including [[The Gulch (Atlanta)|The Gulch]], and following the rail corridor east alongside [[Underground Atlanta]] and terminating at Jesse Hill, Jr. Drive SE (one block southeast of Piedmont Ave.) The Gulch would be covered with parking and transit underneath and open space on top.<ref>[http://www.atlantadowntown.com/_files/docs/greenline-fact-sheet.pdf Green Line Fact Sheet, Central Atlanta Progress]</ref>

